    {
      "id": "b1000001",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 500,
      "y": 20,
      "width": 360,
      "height": 140,
      "text": "# 教学 Agent\n\n目标：懂教材、稳上下文、按教学策略行动，并逐步个性化。",
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "b1000002",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 40,
      "y": 260,
      "width": 280,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "## AIRI\n输入输出层\n语音识别 / 文本 / TTS / Live2D / 流式回复",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "b1000003",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 400,
      "y": 240,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 180,
      "text": "## LangGraph\n短期课堂状态\n回合路由\n工具调度\n记忆写回",
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "b1000004",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 820,
      "y": 240,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 180,
      "text": "## 教学策略层\n讲解\n提示\n纠错\n追问\n回顾前置知识",
      "color": "2"
    },
    {
      "id": "b1000005",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1220,
      "y": 220,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 160,
      "text": "## LightRAG\n教材结构\nTeachingBlock\n范围受控检索",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "b1000006",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1220,
      "y": 460,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 160,
      "text": "## SimpleMem\n学生画像\n重复错误\n提示偏好",
      "color": "6"
    },
    {
      "id": "b1000007",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 820,
      "y": 500,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 140,
      "text": "## 模型层\nLLM\nEmbedding\n可选重排器",
      "color": "3"
    },
    {
      "id": "b1000008",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1560,
      "y": 200,
      "width": 220,
      "height": 220,
      "text": "## TeachingBlock\n教材教学单元\nscene_summary\nteaching_goal\ncore_patterns\nallowed_answer_scope",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "b1000009",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1560,
      "y": 470,
      "width": 220,
      "height": 230,
      "text": "## 学生记忆链\nLessonTrace\nTeachingUnit\nLearningCrystal\nEVOLVES",
      "color": "6"
    },
    {
      "id": "b2000001",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 1140,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 220,
      "text": "## 回合路由\nanswer_question\nask_knowledge\nask_help\nnavigation\nsocial\nmeta_learning",
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "b2000002",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 500,
      "y": 1140,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 220,
      "text": "## 本地优先判定\n当前 block\n当前 page\n当前 unit\n默认不做全局检索",
      "color": "2"
    },
    {
      "id": "b2000003",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 920,
      "y": 1140,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 180,
      "text": "## 检索扩域\nblock -> page -> unit -> global\n只在必要时向外扩展",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "b2000004",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1320,
      "y": 1140,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 180,
      "text": "## 记忆写回\n提炼真正有价值的学习事实\n不保存每一条原始对话",
      "color": "6"
    },
    {
      "id": "b2000005",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 480,
      "y": 1450,
      "width": 560,
      "height": 220,
      "text": "## MVP\n1. 试点单元转为 TeachingBlock\n2. LessonState + 路由\n3. 范围受控的 LightRAG\n4. 学生答案判定\n5. AIRI 回复与动作输出",
      "color": "1"
    },
